OL,3,CLeicester City lose appeal against six-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,FLeicester City have lost their appeal
OL,7,Fagainst a six-point deduction in the
OL,8,FChampionship.
OL,10,FThe club were docked points in
OL,11,FFebruary for breaching financial
OL,12,Frules. It saw the Foxes fall from 17th
OL,13,Fto 20th.
OL,15,FBut they have since dropped even
OL,16,Ffurther, fighting relegation with five
OL,17,Fgames left to play.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
