OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775833867
OL,3,CLeicester City lose appeal against six-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,FIt came after a recommendation by an
OL,7,FIndependent Commission, which found
OL,8,Fthe club had breached the EFL's Profit
OL,9,Fand Sustainability Rules in the three
OL,10,Fyears ending June 2024
OL,12,FThe club said the Appeal Board's
OL,13,Fdecision is "accepted by the club".
OL,15,FIt added in a statement: "With the
OL,16,Fmatter now at an end and five games of
OL,17,Fthe season remaining, everyone at the
OL,18,FClub is fully focused on the matches
OL,19,Fin front of us and on shaping the
OL,20,Foutcome of our season through our
OL,21,Fresults on the pitch.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1775833867
OL,3,CLeicester City lose appeal against six-
OL,4,Cpoint deduction
OL,6,F"We know this has been a challenging
OL,7,Fperiod, and we thank our supporters
OL,8,Ffor the backing they continue to give
OL,9,Fthe team.
OL,11,F"The responsibility now is to ensure
OL,12,Fthese remaining games are approached
OL,13,Fwith the focus and intent our current
OL,14,Fsituation demands."
OL,16,FThe Premier League also lodged its own
OL,17,Fappeal, which was dismissed.
OL,19,FIt suggested a further one point
OL,20,Fdeduction for the club's late
OL,21,Fsubmission of its Annual Accounts.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
